reviewText:
Fairy tales.  Jenny is a slave living inside a corded lamp.  Once out alive, she sexually fulfills her army master.  Similarly, her male companion lives in a small wooden box.  He comes out alive too.  Ha Ha, he is to serve two women in a different house.
The second movie is about a cave girl and her male companion, surviving through dinosaur danger.  Teasing sex scenes are entertaining.

Noticeably these actors and actresses are hardcore labeled.  Meaning two movies may have been edited to "R" version.  OR intentionally produced as is.  The erotic nature through touching and simulating sex are seen as soft core.  One low price for two hot movies is a a steal.  Go for it.
